To run this project do the following
Download the "diff-me" file from the src folder

and the run the command by followed by flags and command
like this :

./diff-me file1.txt file2.txt

You can use following flags
-y - for side by side output
-c - for context output
-w - ignore all the white spaces
-b - ignore changes in amount of white space and trailing whitespace
-i - ignore case
./diff-me -y file1.txt file2.txt
./diff-me -c file1.txt file2.txt
./diff-me -w -b -i file1.txt file2.txt  (use these 3 flags in anycombination with -y -c or default diff)
